data.description: Short Sale. BANK PRICE APPROVED. Back on the market. Great Location! 3 bedroom, 2 bath home, featuring a spacious open floor plan. Plenty of natural light throughout the house. This home includes a walk-in closet in the master bathroom, a glass shower in the master bathroom, gorgeous 36-inch tall kitchen cabinets, vinyl fencing around the backyard, and a beautifully spacious driveway for extra parking. Amenities include a clubhouse, zero-entry community pool, fitness center, tennis courts, pickleball court, and volleyball, play areas, dog park, and soccer field. You can also enjoy a walk on the nature trails throughout this community! Just a few minutes from Downtown Kissimmee, Florida Turnpike, Airport, VA Hospital, THE LOOP Shopping area, and Sunrail Train,  30 minutes All Theme Parks
